					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">If you're really looking for a cheap option, sacrifice one Genesis controller by removing the IC and wiring the eight outputs directly. It won't be a compatible pinout with the existing DE9-joystick game consoles (none support 8 digital outputs).<br /><br />The Neo Geo <a href="https://www.gamesx.com/controldata/superneo.htm" class="postlink">DA15 port</a> could be worth mimicking instead.</div>

